Here is a link with a tutorial to set up the network: http://examples.digi.com/get-started/basic-xbee-802-15-4-chat/

Here are instructions to set up point to point communication for 2 XBees. Open CoolTerm, find device, and start comm.

On the first one:
1. Options - select device - ok
2. Type +++ (don't press enter)
3. ATID2171 (ENTER)
4. ATMY1 (ENTER)
5. ATDL0 (ENTER)
6. ATBD3 (ENTER)
7. ATWR (ENTER)

On the second one, enter:
1. Options - select device - ok
2. Type +++ (don't press enter)
3. ATID2171 (ENTER)
4. ATMY0 (ENTER)
5. ATDL1 (ENTER)
6. ATBD3 (ENTER)
7. ATWR (ENTER)

